        public void init(AI[] ais,
                 java.lang.String id)
        Initializes a new Game based on the player names.

        This constructor will instantiate (but not populate) all attributes of this Game instance.

        Parameters:
        ais - Names of each current player (ordered by login time)
        id - The game id.
